title: Digital Elevation Model Phase 1
description:
Phase1 (2010 - 2017) Statewide LiDAR-derived Digital Elevation Model.

This dataset provides access to a LiDAR-derived 5 Foot Digital Elevation Model (DEM) for the entire Commonwealth of Kentucky. LiDAR was collected at Quality Level 3 or better from 2010 â€“ 2017 for KYAPED project areas while no snow was on the ground and rivers were at or below normal levels.
